---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken Thigh with Roasted Potatoes and Creamy Dill Sauce
description: We’ve cracked the code to creating a crowd-pleasing dinner! Everyone loves a good cream sauce – especially one that’s spiked with a touch of mustard and fresh dill! It’s the perfect addition to juicy pan-seared chicken.
